       <div class="tab-collage__content-pink {{ section.settings.text_alignment }} mobile-{{ section.settings.mobile_text_alignment }} page-width">
            <h3 class="collage-pinktxt">Clinically proven results. 100% natural ingredients. Innovative red algae gel suitable for the face and body</h3>

